mination</li><li>instructors must have an accreditation as a technician for air-conditioning equipment in certain motor vehicles and be under the direction of a person who holds a bachelor's degree in automotive technology, a master's degree in engineering, a master's degree in industrial sciences or a master's degree in bioengineering, or a person with at least three years of demonstrable experience in providing training in that subject</li><li>compose a regulatory examination jury.</li></ul></li></ul><p>More info on the recognition conditions can be found in <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058&amp;woLang=nl\">art. 8 (general recognition conditions)</a> and <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=68918&amp;woLang=nl\">art. 24/7 VLAREL (special recognition conditions)</a>. </p><h3>Period of validity and obligations</h3><p>Recognition as a training centre is valid for <strong>an indefinite period of</strong> time. However, a recognised training centre must fulfil a number of obligations (= user requirements) in order to maintain its recognition.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-opleidingscentra-voor-de-technicus-klimaatregelingssytemen-in-bepaalde-motorvoertuigen\">More info on the obligations for approved training centres for the technician for air-conditioning equipment in certain motor vehicles.</a></p>"},"naam":{"en":"Requirements","nl-BE-x-formal":"Voorwaarden","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Voorwaarden","en-x-generated":"Conditions","nl":"Voorwaarden"},"@type":"Voorwaarde","order":0}],"procedures":[{"naam":{"en-x-generated":"Procedure","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Procedure","nl":"Procedure","nl-BE-x-formal":"Procedure","en":"Procedure"},"beschrijving":{"en":"<p>Request your recognition from the Flemish administration.</p><ul><li><p>Download the <a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/raw/upload/v1654023906/191004_Aanvraag_tot_erkenning_als_opleidingscentrum_voor_TKM_wexzfe.docx\">application form</a>. On the application form, you must demonstrate that the training centre meets the conditions for recognition.</p></li><li><p>Submit the necessary documents to the Flemish administration.</p><ul><li><strong>If you have a Belgian eID</strong>: submit your application and receipt via the <a href=\"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/natuur-milieu-en-klimaat/erkenning-als-technicus-deskundige-opleidingscentrum-of-labo/erkenningenloket-omgeving\">online recognition desk</a> of the Department of Environment and Spatial Development (click on ‘Ga naar het erkenningenloket’; log in with eID).</li><li><strong>If you do not have a Belgian eID:</strong> you should submit your application by registered letter to Departement Omgeving, Koning Albert II-laan 20/bus 8, 1000 Brussel, to the attention of Team Erkenningen, Afdeling GOP.</li></ul></li></ul><p>The competent unit will handle your request. This could involve a site visit. The leading official of the Energy and Climate Agency of Flanders reaches a decision within 90 days, starting from the day after the submission of the complete application file.</p>","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>Vraag jouw erkenning aan bij de Vlaamse overheid.</p><ul><li>Download het <a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/raw/upload/v1654023906/191004_Aanvraag_tot_erkenning_als_opleidingscentrum_voor_TKM_wexzfe.docx\">aanvraagformulier</a> en vul het in. Met dat aanvraagformulier moet je aantonen dat het opleidingscentrum voldoet aan de erkenningsvoorwaarden.</li><li>Bezorg de nodige documenten aan de Vlaamse overheid<ul><li>Je beschikt over een Belgische eID: dien jouw aanvraag in via het <a href=\"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/natuur-milieu-en-klimaat/erkenning-als-technicus-deskundige-opleidingscentrum-of-labo/erkenningenloket-omgeving\">online erkenningenloket van het Departement Omgeving</a> (klik op “Ga naar het erkenningenloket”; aanmelden met eID).</li><li>Je beschikt niet over een Belgische eID: stuur jouw aanvraag met een aang